{"data": [{"id": "4742554", "title": "Korn Ferry 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Korn Ferry in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106058\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742554-korn-ferry-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:39:47"}, {"id": "4742541", "title": "SentinelOne: Scaling Faster And Creating Value", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female climber on a rocky wall\" data-id=\"1189534859\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"921px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Buena Vista Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I have analyzed the cybersecurity sector via several ETFs such as <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733562-bug-dont-bug-me-rating-downgrade\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733562-bug-dont-bug-me-rating-downgrade\" target=\"_blank\">Global X Cybersecurity</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BUG\" title=\"Global X Funds - Global X Cybersecurity ETF\">BUG</a>) and the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4677154-cibr-underperforming-the-cybersecurity-sector\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4677154-cibr-underperforming-the-cybersecurity-sector\" target=\"_blank\">First Trust NASDAQ Cybersecurity</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIBR\" title=\"First Trust Nasdaq CEA Cybersecurity ETF\">CIBR</a>), which did not instill me with enthusiasm or conviction</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742541-sentinelone-stock-scaling-faster-creating-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:33:45"}, {"id": "4742539", "title": "China Yuchai International: Significant R&D Focus And Rising Exposure To ESG Trend, Yet Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Closeup of team members examine ESG-related documents, pointing and discussing investment strategies for sustainable and renewable energy resources. Eco-Friendly Business Discussing ESG Goals.\" data-id=\"2148427753\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/g